crude (1.2.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Add crude-xero: command-line client for Xero accounting over the official
    OAuth2 APIs. Covers the Accounting API (accounts, bank transactions and
    transfers, contacts and groups, invoices, bills, credit notes, items,
    payments, purchase orders, quotes, manual journals, tax rates, tracking
    categories, reports, attachments and history) with list/get/create/update/
    delete, first-page listing plus --all and --limit, and multi-tenant
    selection (--tenant). The one-time `crude-xero auth` runs a browser consent
    (localhost loopback, or --manual paste); the rotating token is stored and
    renewed automatically.
  * Durable token store: site tokens now persist under $XDG_STATE_HOME/crude
    (default ~/.local/state/crude) via a shared crude_common.statestore, so they
    survive a reboot; crude-atdw, crude-skal and crude-sonas adopt it.

 -- Weiwu Zhang <a@colourful.land>  Wed, 17 Jun 2026 11:00:20 +1000

crude (1.1.2) unstable; urgency=medium

  * crude-rezdy: full CRUD over the Rezdy Supplier API. Create, update and
    delete products and availability sessions; manage bookings, customers,
    extras and pickup lists; assign products to categories/rates and sessions
    to resources; manifest check-in; voucher/company reads. Previously the
    crude-rezdy client was read-only.
  * crude-atdw: add `listing create` (POST /api/listings) to create a listing
    from a JSON object; it starts as a draft until submitted.
  * crude-skal: add the benefit resource (the global Skål benefits register).
  * install-claude-command now advertises the new crude-rezdy write verbs and
    crude-atdw listing create.

 -- Weiwu Zhang <a@colourful.land>  Tue, 16 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0000

crude (1.1.1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Add crude-sonas: command-line client for Sonas wedding-venue software.
    Core enquiry verbs cover event lifecycle, guests, timelines, notes,
    messages, documents, terms, service bookings, transactions, and invoices.
    T2 scheduling (availability, appointment, tasting); T3 catalog reads
    (supplier, service, drinks-package, package, template, category, venue,
    user, report); finance and mail verbs; live smoke-test suite.

 -- Weiwu Zhang <a@colourful.land>  Thu, 11 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0000

crude (1.1.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Add crude-deputy: command-line client for Deputy workforce management.
    Curated sub-apps for employee, roster, area, timesheet, and leave; a
    generic resource sub-app reaches any Deputy object with QUERY operators,
    schema info, and full CRUD; `me` shows the token owner.
  * Multi-account support across all site CLIs: the bare [site] section is the
    default account, [site.<name>] subtables are named accounts, selected with
    --account / -a or $CRUDE_ACCOUNT.
  * crude-rezdy: timezone is now a required config field; date filters convert
    the typed day to UTC before comparing against Rezdy's dateUpdated timestamps.

 -- Weiwu Zhang <a@colourful.land>  Sat, 30 May 2026 00:00:00 +0200

crude (1.0.2) unstable; urgency=medium

  * crude-rezdy booking: add `cancellations` subcommand — filters by
    cancellation date (dateUpdated) with columns for product, session,
    paid/total, refund count, and internal notes.
  * crude-rezdy booking list: add --updated-from / --updated-to (client-side
    filter on dateUpdated) and --all (auto-pagination); improve default table
    to show product, session date, paid/total, and last-updated date.
  * crude-rezdy: add paginate() to the API client for auto-pagination.
  * Claude command updated to document new subcommand and flags.

